m\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/03\/16\/khatam-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":25350,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Jannah: Last deeds are righteous, enter Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 16, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Hudhayfah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever declares there is no God but Allah, seeking the countenance of Allah as his last deed, he will enter Paradise. Whoever fasts a day, seeking the countenance of Allah as his last deed, he will enter Paradise. Whoever\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26755,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/08\/15\/sujud-sajdah-in-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":25350,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Sujud: Allah expiates sins by prostration in prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 15, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Ubadah ibn al-Samit reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNo servant prostrates for the sake of Allah but that Allah will record for him one good deed, erase one bad deed, and raise his status by a degree. Thus, perform many prostrations.\u201d Source: Sunan\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24522,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/03\/16\/house-paradise-husn-khuluq\/","url_meta":{"origin":25350,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Adab: House in paradise for those with good character","aut